282,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:16:18.000Z","msg":"其實去黨鐵商場唱歌嗌口號仲好，影響佢租務收入仲好。<br />\n<br />\n跳下閘影響唔到黨鐵。"},{"pid":"19ac7bbc6f5d461bc2f48ca74ea7736991889c18","tid":1561282,"uid":46309,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"今日在大圍想跳，離遠見到有條木嘴望實度閘，心諗仲唔係狗？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJvhu9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJvhu9k.jpg&h=d427fd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁好啦，算我當黑，我去第邊跳。<br />\n<br />\n去第個出口跳完返去望下佢，<br />\n鴉...... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢仲啤鳩返我.... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔撚撚你都對唔住自己啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcSDeBA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcSDeBA.png&h=ffbfa8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cXXEiYewaEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcXXEiYewaEo&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=4c3c0bea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cXXEiYewaEo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n█ █ █ █有冇跳閘都入黎聽我講兩句，唔該<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547201</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n████ 明明港鐵係公共服務，點解唔正面表態，而去坐巴士？港豬們想逃避到幾時？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRkOwS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRkOwS</a>"},{"pid":"228d7d3a4eeaf8113a8c08a2919c89f4d60ac69f","tid":1561282,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2094bd2125534896c39d516b1dd5753bcc50ac0","tid":1561282,"uid":73100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"呢2日係咁比藍屍拍片影大頭 再加埋黑警個報料whatsapp 我真係好擔心有手足因爲跳閘而比狗搞<br />\n大家目的係為左令到黨鐵減少車費收入姐 有時見到d廢老扮拍卡跟住人地尾入閘 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家千祈唔好學呀！</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"你搞錯左<br />\n主要唔係錢 